Package: BetaMixture
Title: Fit Beta Mixture Densities
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Matthew",
           family = "Palmeri",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "matthewpalmeri@outlook.com")
Description: This package contains functions related to fitting mixtures of beta distributions. Included in this are functions relating to pdfs for mixture of beta distributions, and methods to fit these to datasets using a modified version of the EM algorithm.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.3)
Imports: 
    dplyr (>= 0.8.3),
    maxLik (>= 1.3-8)
